rdemain.com">Legerdemain</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=terailgrimtooth>Terail Grimtooth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 57<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/19/02 10:37:46 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4446.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: proc's mandatory for aggro?</span><hr size=1> I use Frostbringer as a agrro wepon and one of my main wepons i carry around. the proc and the 12/22 is nice!! but anyways just carry around with you a procing wepon its nice to have <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <p>Terail Grimtooth<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=243427"> My Gear</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
42 Troll Warrior<br>
Proud Member of Da Skurge!</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=terailgrimtooth>Terail Grimtooth</A> at: 11/19/02 10:41:15 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=koguinfearlesswarrior>Koguin Fearless Warrior</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/19/02 11:43:51 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4446.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: proc's mandatory for aggro?</span><hr size=1> i'd say keep the WC im prim hand and get horn on offhand.<br>
save up and get a CoF.......<br>
but then again CoF's price killed more than one ) <p>&lt;a href=&quot;www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=38622&quot;&gt;Koguin Fearless&lt;/a&gt;</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=sulvar>Sulvar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 127<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/19/02 12:24:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4446.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: proc's mandatory for aggro?</span><hr size=1> IMO procs aren't required for agro in any xp group.  I have been using my windblade (slow 2hs weapon, no proc) full time lately and I have no problems with agro in any of the tier 1-2 planes in PoP.  Really with the way taunt works now (hint it rules compared to before the taunt fix) agro is much less of a problem all around. <p>Gartuff &lt;Ex Tempore&gt;<br>
